summary: This document is an email chain from July 9, 2019, forwarding an edited version of a 'Hotline_Tracker' spreadsheet intended for the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (SDNY). It indicates coordination on providing information to federal prosecutors.

events.title: Hotline Tracker Prepared for SDNY
events.description: An email is sent forwarding an edited version of a 'Hotline_Tracker' spreadsheet to be sent to the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (SDNY).

keyFacts: A 'Hotline_Tracker' spreadsheet was being prepared for federal prosecutors (SDNY) on July 9, 2019.
The document indicates ongoing coordination and information sharing related to the Epstein investigation.
The email chain shows an internal review process ('edited version') before sending information to authorities.
